description:
Live like a New Yorker in this quaint and updated one bedroom in the heart of Astoria! Less than 10 minutes walking distance to 4 subway lines. Jump on the subway and be in Times Square or Central Park in 15 minutes! Great local restaurants and bars are nearby walking distance if you'd like to keep it local and explore Astoria in the borough of Queens!

Enjoy visiting New York in this updated Astoria ground floor apartment, minutes from Manhattan! 

Recently updated, this charming one bedroom is your perfect stay! Once you enter the apartment thru your private entrance, you are greeted by the sleeping area with a comfy pull down bed. 

In the center of the apartment is the living area, two sofas which also fold down into beds. The living space is perfect for relaxing after a long day of sight seeing, complete with Roku TV and an electric fireplace! 

Off the living space is the remodeled full bathroom with a shower tub combo, heated floors and a heated towel rack!

Just past the living area is the newly updated kitchen, full of cookware and dish ware for preparing a home cooked meal! Enjoy your meal at the large bistro set in the living area. 

Fully stocked Keurig is provided for our guests convenience.

Beautifully updated and private, this one bedroom apartment is your perfect NYC getaway!

Apartment only.

We like to respect guests' privacy but please let us know if you need anything!

Our neighborhood is centrally located to all famous NYC sites and local eats!  Start off your New York day in Central Park, only a 15 minute subway ride! Want to check out the most famous part of the city? Times Square is an 18 minute subway ride. Don't forget to visit the top of the Empire State building near Herald Square.

Less than 10 minute walk to 4 subway lines (the N or W at Broadway and the M or R at Steinway Street). You can reach Manhattan in 10 minutes!

*Laundry
Although there is no washer or dryer, there are two laundromats on the corner which provide drop off service.

*Parking
Only public street parking is available which may be difficult to find during certain times of the day.
house_rules:
• Check in time is 3PM - 11PM
• No parties or events
• Not suitable for pets
• No smoking

Please respect our neighbors and a quiet time between 11PM-7AM.
